mmunication environment.\\n- Subtle glowing rims accentuate each character.\\n\\nACTION AND CAMERA MOTION \'97\\n1. Leonardo dynamically slashes air to manipulate floating time calendar holograms.\\n2. Donatello confidently points his bo staff at files, as data cubes shift and rotate around him.\\n3. Michelangelo rides his light surfboard, energetically interacting with chat messages that appear with playful animations.\\n\\nCINEMATOGRAPHY \'97\\n- Lighting setups use colored glows matching each turtle\'92s mask color to highlight their zones.\\n- Emotional tone balances action, intellect, and work focus with vibrancy and energy.\\n- Color palette is diverse: blues for Leonardo, purples for Donatello, oranges for Michelangelo, reds for Raphael, and warm golds for Splinter.\\n\\nAUDIO \'97\\n- Voices for each turtle: confident and task-focused tone.\\n- Language: English.\\n- Dialogue examples (Leonardo): \\"Time is our ally.\\"\\n- Dialogue examples (Donatello): \\"All files are under control.\\"\\n- Dialogue examples (Michelangelo): \\"Surf\'92s up, let\'92s chat!\\"\\n- Dialogue examples (Raphael): \\"Tasks incoming, let's execute!\\"\\n- Ambient: soft digital hums, subtle mechanical and electronic beeps.\\n- No music.\\n\\nSTYLE \'97\\n- Hyper-realistic comic art style with sharp, clean lines and detailed textures.\\n- 4K quality with vivid, saturated colors.\\n- No subtitles, captions, or text overlays beyond comic cell labels already described.\\n- No scene cuts or transitions; a unified comic page composition.","quality":"basic","aspect_ratio":"16:9","duration":8,"model":"veo-3-1-preview","enhance_prompt":true,"scene_cut":false,"mode":"input_images","input_image":\{"id":"124799d9-b167-482c-9f23-59ca49efdb5e","url":"https://d8j0ntlcm91z4.cloudfront.net/user_37APpNltMWeKwUOXZWyJZVurKd1/hf_20260119_031953_124799d9-b167-482c-9f23-59ca49efdb5e.png","type":"nano_banana_2_job"\},"end_input_image":null,"style_input_image":null,"reference_input_images":null,"motion_id"